---
import ToolLayout from '../../components/ToolLayout.astro';
---
<ToolLayout title="Drywall Repair Cost Calculator" description="Calculate drywall repair and installation costs by type and size of damage." icon="üß±" category="Cost Estimators" categorySlug="cost-estimators">
  <div slot="calculator">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div><label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#1B4965] mb-1">Repair Type</label>
        <select id="type" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#FF6B35]">
          <option value="75,200">Small hole (nail/screw, under 2")</option>
          <option value="150,400" selected>Medium hole (fist-size, 2-6")</option>
          <option value="250,600">Large hole (6-12")</option>
          <option value="400,1000">Section replacement (12"+)</option>
          <option value="1.50,3.50">New drywall installation (per sq ft)</option>
          <option value="1.00,2.50">Skim coat / texture match (per sq ft)</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div><label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#1B4965] mb-1">Number of Repairs / Sq Ft</label><input type="number" id="qty" value="3" min="1" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#FF6B35] focus:border-transparent" /></div>
      <div><label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#1B4965] mb-1">Include Painting?</label>
        <select id="paint" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#FF6B35]">
          <option value="0">No (patch only)</option>
          <option value="75" selected>Yes, patch area ($50-100 per spot)</option>
          <option value="300">Yes, full wall ($200-400)</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button onclick="calc()" class="mt-6 bg-[#FF6B35] hover:bg-[#e55a2b] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors w-full md:w-auto">Estimate Drywall Cost</button>
    <div id="result" class="mt-6 hidden"><div class="bg-[#1B4965]/5 rounded-xl p-6"><h3 class="font-bold text-[#1B4965] text-lg mb-3">Drywall Cost Estimate</h3><div id="res"></div></div></div>
  </div>
  <Fragment slot="content">
    <h2>Drywall Repair Costs</h2>
    <p>Small drywall repairs (nail holes, small dents) are one of the easiest DIY projects. A $10 patch kit handles most small holes. Professional handyman repairs start at <strong>$75-150 per patch</strong>.</p>
    <h2>DIY Drywall Tips</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>‚úÖ Small holes: Spackle + sand + paint (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>‚úÖ Medium holes: Self-adhesive mesh patch + joint compound</li>
      <li>‚ö†Ô∏è Large holes: California patch or new drywall piece ‚Äî more skill needed</li>
      <li>The hardest part is matching the existing texture (orange peel, knockdown, smooth)</li>
    </ul>
  </Fragment>
</ToolLayout>
<script is:inline>
function calc(){
  const[lo,hi]=document.getElementById('type').value.split(',').map(Number);
  const qty=parseFloat(document.getElementById('qty').value);
  const paint=parseFloat(document.getElementById('paint').value);
  const costLo=Math.round(lo*qty+paint);const costHi=Math.round(hi*qty+paint);
  document.getElementById('result').classList.remove('hidden');
  document.getElementById('res').innerHTML=`
    <div class="text-center"><div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FF6B35]">$${costLo.toLocaleString()} ‚Äì $${costHi.toLocaleString()}</div><div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">${qty} repair${qty>1?'s':''} + ${paint>0?'painting':'no painting'}</div></div>`;
}
</script>
